Story_Texts.SourceString: We need to stop Kilthor and rescue Kailani!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: We need to stop Kilthor and rescue Kailani!

Story_Texts.SourceString: Kilthor holds her captive on peaks of the Abyssal Precipice.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Kilthor holds her captive on peaks of the Abyssal Precipice.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Zerath's stronghold is near. His power will be immensely strong here.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Zerath's stronghold is near. His power will be immensely strong here.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Let's put this demon in his place!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Let's put this demon in his place!

Story_Texts.SourceString: Kilthor is one of Zerath's most powerful generals. We will need to be smart to defeat him.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Kilthor is one of Zerath's most powerful generals. We will need to be smart to defeat him.

Story_Texts.SourceString: My strategy is to stab him with my wonderful fiery sword until he stops moving!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: My strategy is to stab him with my wonderful fiery sword until he stops moving!

Story_Texts.SourceString: You don't take one of my friends and live to brag about it.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: You don't take one of my friends and live to brag about it.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Drake is all fired up! But is mew really a mage? Let's go!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Drake is all fired up! But is mew really a mage? Let's go!
